Case 1:20-cr-00330-PAE Document 193 Filed 04/02/21 Page 1 of 1
UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT SOUTHERN DISTRICT OF NEW YORK
United States of America,
-v-
Ghislain Maxwell,
Defendant.
20-CR-330 (AJN)
ORDER
ALISON J. NATHAN, District Judge:
An arraignment on the S2 Superseding Indictment and a status conference is hereby tentatively scheduled for April 16, 2021. As requested by the Defendant, the proceeding will take place in person. The Court is making logistical arrangements and will provide more information when it is available.
The Government is ORDERED to respond to the issues raised in the Defendant's March 31, 2021 letter, Dkt. No. 192, by April 9, 2021.
SO ORDERED.
Dated: April 2, 2021 New York, New York
ALISON J. NATHAN United States District Judge
